---

<BaseLayout title="Cenník - Papi Hair Design | Transparentné ceny kaderníckych služieb" description="Transparentný cenník kaderníckych služieb v Košiciach. Žiadne skryté poplatky, profesionálne služby a výhodné balíčky.">
  <Header />

  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-50 to-white">
    <div class="px-4 mx-auto max-w-7xl sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center">
        <h1 class="mb-6 text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 md:text-5xl">
          Transparentný <span class="text-primary-600">cenník</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-8 text-xl text-gray-600">
          Žiadne skryté poplatky ani nepríjemné prekvapenia. Všetky ceny sú stanovené vopred a konečné.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Pricing Cards -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="px-4 mx-auto max-w-7xl sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <!-- Dámske služby -->
      <h2 class="mb-12 text-3xl font-bold text-center text-gray-900">Dámsky cenník</h2>

      <div class="mb-16">
        <h3 class="pb-2 mb-8 text-2xl font-semibold border-b-2 text-primary-600 border-primary-200">Strihy a styling</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-4">
          <li><strong>Strih</strong> (1 h) – <span class="font-bold text-primary-600">od 30 €</span> <span class="text-gray-500">(umytie, strihanie, styling)</span></li>
          <li><strong>Finálny styling</strong> (30 min.) – <span class="font-bold text-primary-600">od 20 €</span> <span class="text-gray-500">(úprava účesu na konkrétnu príležitosť)</span></li>
          <li><strong>Spoločenský účes</strong> (1 h) – <span class="font-bold text-primary-600">40 €</span> <span class="text-gray-500">(detailný styling na spoločenské udalosti)</span></li>
          <li><strong>Fúkaná (polodlhé vlasy)</strong> (30 min.) – <span class="font-bold text-primary-600">20 €</span></li>
          <li><strong>Fúkaná (dlhé vlasy)</strong> (1 h) – <span class="font-bold text-primary-600">30 €</span></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="mb-16">
        <h3 class="pb-2 mb-8 text-2xl font-semibold border-b-2 text-primary-600 border-primary-200">Copríky a špeciálne účesy</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-4">
          <li><strong>Copíky / braids</strong> (4 h) – <span class="font-bold text-primary-600">od 30 €</span> <span class="text-gray-500">(komplexné pletenie a styling)</span></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="mb-16">
        <h3 class="pb-2 mb-8 text-2xl font-semibold border-b-2 text-primary-600 border-primary-200">Ošetrenie a keratín</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-4">
          <li><strong>Brazílsky keratín</strong> (3 h) – <span class="font-bold text-primary-600">od 130 €</span> <span class="text-gray-500">(hlboká regenerácia a vyhladenie vlasov)</span></li>
          <li><strong>Methamorphyc exclusive</strong> (1 h 30 min.) – <span class="font-bold text-primary-600">50 €</span> <span class="text-gray-500">(exkluzívna kúra s intenzívnou starostlivosťou)</span></li>
          <li><strong>Methamorphyc quick</strong> (1 h) – <span class="font-bold text-primary-600">od 35 €</span> <span class="text-gray-500">(rýchla regenerácia a lesk vlasov)</span></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="mb-16">
        <h3 class="pb-2 mb-8 text-2xl font-semibold border-b-2 text-primary-600 border-primary-200">Farbenie a odlesky</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-4">
          <li><strong>Farbenie (celé vlasy)</strong> (2 h) – <span class="font-bold text-primary-600">70 €</span></li>
          <li><strong>Farbenie (odrasty)</strong> (1 h 30 min.) – <span class="font-bold text-primary-600">45 €</span></li>
          <li><strong>Farbenie + strih (celé vlasy)</strong> (2 h) – <span class="font-bold text-primary-600">90 €</span></li>
          <li><strong>Farbenie + strih (odrasty)</strong> (2 h) – <span class="font-bold text-primary-600">60 €</span></li>
          <li><strong>Zosvetľovanie / gumovanie farby</strong> (4 h) – <span class="font-bold text-primary-600">od 160 €</span></li>
          <li><strong>Čistenie odleskov</strong> (3 h) – <span class="font-bold text-primary-600">od 100 €</span></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="mb-16">
        <h3 class="pb-2 mb-8 text-2xl font-semibold border-b-2 text-primary-600 border-primary-200">Melíry a balayage</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-4">
          <li><strong>Melír (odrasty)</strong> (3 h) – <span class="font-bold text-primary-600">od 120 €</span></li>
          <li><strong>Melír (celé vlasy)</strong> (4 h) – <span class="font-bold text-primary-600">od 150 €</span></li>
          <li><strong>Balayage (doplnenie odrastov)</strong> (3 h) – <span class="font-bold text-primary-600">od 120 €</span></li>
          <li><strong>Balayage (celé vlasy)</strong> (4 h) – <span class="font-bold text-primary-600">od 150 €</span></li>
          <li><strong>Airtouch (doplnenie odrastov)</strong> (4 h) – <span class="font-bold text-primary-600">od 140 €</span></li>
          <li><strong>Airtouch (celé vlasy)</strong> (5 h) – <span class="font-bold text-primary-600">od 170 €</span></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="mb-16">
        <h3 class="pb-2 mb-8 text-2xl font-semibold border-b-2 text-primary-600 border-primary-200">Predlžovanie vlasov</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-4">
          <li><strong>Napojenie TAPE IN</strong> (1 h) – <span class="font-bold text-primary-600">od 40 €</span></li>
          <li><strong>Prepojenie TAPE IN</strong> (2 h 30 min.) – <span class="font-bold text-primary-600">od 120 €</span></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Pánske služby -->
      <h2 class="mb-12 text-3xl font-bold text-center text-gray-900">Pánsky cenník</h2>

      <div class="mb-16">
        <h3 class="pb-2 mb-8 text-2xl font-semibold border-b-2 text-primary-600 border-primary-200">Strihy a úprava vlasov</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-4">
          <li><strong>Pánsky strih</strong> – <span class="font-bold text-primary-600">19 €</span></li>
          <li><strong>Junior strih</strong> – <span class="font-bold text-primary-600">15 €</span></li>
          <li><strong>Vlasy + brada</strong> – <span class="font-bold text-primary-600">27 €</span></li>
          <li><strong>Pánsky špeciál</strong> – <span class="font-bold text-primary-600">50 €</span></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="mb-16">
        <h3 class="pb-2 mb-8 text-2xl font-semibold border-b-2 text-primary-600 border-primary-200">Brada a fúzy</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-4">
          <li><strong>Úprava brady</strong> – <span class="font-bold text-primary-600">12 €</span></li>
          <li><strong>Farbenie brady</strong> – <span class="font-bold text-primary-600">10 €</span></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="mb-16">
        <h3 class="pb-2 mb-8 text-2xl font-semibold border-b-2 text-primary-600 border-primary-200">Farbenie a špeciálne techniky</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-4">
          <li><strong>Tónovanie šedín</strong> (30 min.) – <span class="font-bold text-primary-600">10 €</span></li>
          <li><strong>Zosvetľovanie vlasov</strong> (1 h 30 min.) – <span class="font-bold text-primary-600">40 €</span></li>
          <li><strong>Trvalá ondulácia</strong> (1 h 30 min.) – <span class="font-bold text-primary-600">40 €</span></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="mb-16">
        <h3 class="pb-2 mb-8 text-2xl font-semibold border-b-2 text-primary-600 border-primary-200">Wellness & starostlivosť</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-4">
          <li><strong>Depilácia nosa</strong> (10 min.) – <span class="font-bold text-primary-600">5 €</span></li>
          <li><strong>Depilácia uší</strong> (10 min.) – <span class="font-bold text-primary-600">5 €</span></li>
          <li><strong>Peeling / čierna maska</strong> (25 min.) – <span class="font-bold text-primary-600">10 €</span></li>
          <li><strong>Ušné sviečky</strong> (20 min.) – <span class="font-bold text-primary-600">10 €</span></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-primary-600">
    <div class="max-w-4xl px-4 mx-auto text-center sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="mb-4 text-3xl font-bold text-white md:text-4xl">
        Chcete presnejšiu cenovú ponuku?
      </h2>
      <p class="mb-8 text-xl text-primary-100">
        Kontaktujte nás pre osobnú konzultáciu a cenovú ponuku šitú na mieru vašim potrebám.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col justify-center gap-4 sm:flex-row">
        <a
          href="/kontakty"
          class="px-8 py-4 text-lg font-semibold transition-all transform bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg text-primary-600 hover:bg-gray-100 hover:scale-105"
        >
          Rezervovať konzultáciu
        </a>
        <a
          href="tel:+421949459624"
          class="px-8 py-4 text-lg font-semibold text-white transition-all border-2 border-white rounded-lg hover:bg-white hover:text-primary-600"
        >
          +421 949 459 624
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Footer />
</BaseLayout>

<style>
 .logo-hero {
   display: block;
   max-width: 180px;
   animation: floatLogo 3s ease-in-out infinite;
 }
 @keyframes floatLogo {
   0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0); }
   50% { transform: translateY(-12px); }
 }
</style>
